				<h3 class="author"><em>by</em> Dirk Stoop</h3>
				<p class="intro">On the eve of the biggest WWDC ever, we&#39;re ready to tell the world about our next app: Kaleidoscope. Come check it out.</p>
				
				
			</div>
			<div class="right_col">
				<p>The past couple of months, we have been working hard on Sofa&#39;s next Mac app: Kaleidoscope. And today we&#39;re ready and excited to tell you a bit about it.</p>

<p>You&#39;ll have to wait for tomorrow to hear about Apple&#39;s next big thing. So now is the perfect time to go check out ours. You won&#39;t regret it. <a href="http://www.kaleidoscopeapp.com">www.kaleidoscopeapp.com</a>.</p>

<div class="align_image_right">
	<img class="no_border" style="margin-bottom:10px" src="http://www.madebysofa.com/media/img/blog/sofas_next_big_thing/kaleidoscope_icon.png" width="420" height="396" alt="An image of Kaleidoscope&#39;s application icon.">
</div>

<p>We&#39;re trying something new in introducing this app, so go take a look and let us know what you think. If you want to learn more, there&#39;s a good chance we can be found at <a href="http://tinyurl.com/map2royale">Caf&eacute; Royale</a>, our favorite San Francisco hangout. You just might be able to bribe us with some drinks. For those attending, have a great WWDC!</p>
